snippet.textDisplay:
Husn tera (j kay liyay)
Hogayay khokhlay alfaaz sabhi,
Jumlay saaray bikhar gayay hayay,
Teri zulfun kay peech-o-kham ki tarah,
Main tasavur main teray ulajh gayaa,

Had-e-khayaal say bhi lout aaya hun khali,
Teray roshan jabeen ki koyee misaal nahi,
Jab huwa teri galiyun say guzarna mera,
Khushboo-e-ishq main lipat gaya wajood mera,

Mainey soocha tha tareef-e-yaar main beshaq,
Likhun ga main koyee taveel sa afsaana,
Hayay afsoos itna wasih andaaz-e-bayaan,
Jho terey soorat o seerat ko bayaan kar pata,
Kahan say aati sukhanwari ki ada aisey,
Mir-o-Ghalib ka agar hota main shagird bhi tou,
Husn tera samata lafzun main mumkin he na tha,

Iss tarah aisa huwa jaan-e-ada,
Hogayee koshishain saari zaaya,
Tumharay naaz-o-ada, husn-o-wafa, jaan-e-aziz,
Meray hunar ki hadoon main kabhi sama na sakhay,
Youn tou qabil nahi hakeer mera ye nazraana, 

Phir bhi kouch aur na soojha garib shair ko,
Aey Mehar keh dey duwaawun say asar ley aayay,
Visaal-e-yaar laayay, 
Karaar laayay, 
Sakoon ley aayay;
 - Jazieray
